  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BE THE HANDS AND FEET OF DARI</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Ark Foundation, Ghana is  launching an appeal to support 80 year old Dari and her 13 year old granddaughter in the Upper West Region. Dari, who suffers from leprosy has very little support for her food and everyday needs. She lives at the outskirts of her village in a hut that is not likely to survive a downpour. The Ark wishes to garner support from people like you who care to give her a decent hut, daily food and a stipend for her health needs.</narrative>
  </description>
